    <fr:title text="Affine morphisms">Affine morphisms</fr:title>
    <fr:taxon>Definition</fr:taxon>
  </fr:frontmatter>
  <fr:mainmatter>
    <html:p>
  We say a map <fr:tex display="inline"><![CDATA[f : X \to  Y]]></fr:tex> between <fr:link href="/schm-86OJ/" title="Scheme" uri="https://charloced.github.io/schm-86OJ/" display-uri="schm-86OJ" type="local">schemes</fr:link> is <html:em>affine</html:em>, if for all affine open <fr:tex display="inline"><![CDATA[\operatorname {Spec} A]]></fr:tex> of <fr:tex display="inline"><![CDATA[Y]]></fr:tex>, <fr:tex display="inline"><![CDATA[f^{-1}(\operatorname {Spec} A)]]></fr:tex> is an affine open in <fr:tex display="inline"><![CDATA[X]]></fr:tex>.
</html:p>
  </fr:mainmatter>
